                   } else { %>
                     <p>We go above and beyond to keep your water crystal clear and your experience stress‑free. The Swim Studs team communicates proactively, arrives on time, and delivers dependable results on every visit—from weekly service to green‑to‑clean recovery and equipment repairs.</p>
                     <p><strong>Let Swim Studs keep your pool sparkling with expert care you can trust.</strong></p>
                   <% }
                 } %>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row mt-5">
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-lg-3">
              <div class="promise-card mb-4">
                <div class="promise-card--image mb-4"></div>
                <div class="d-flex">
                  <div class="promise-card--number"><span>01</span></div>
